.cs 7 on
.item 'SET UMESSAGE Command' 'Added 07/08/82 by LSO'
.boxon
SET UMESSAGE [message]
.boxoff

.* DESCRIPTION
Required Privileges:  OPERATOR

The SET UMESSAGE (or SET UMSG) command sets the user message that would be
displayed to users when they logon.

.* SELECT 'SET UMESSAGE Command Options'
.us Option Descriptions

.* OPTION MESSAGE
.ix message 'on SET UMESSAGE Command'
message\\\\\\\\\a one line message that cannot exceed 255 characters.  If
                there is no message, the user message will be removed.
.cs 7 off
